headline: Wells Fargo Increases PT on The Pennant Group Stock, Keeps Equal Weight Rating
summary: The Pennant Group, Inc. (NASDAQ:PNTG) is one of the 12 Small Cap Stocks with High Upside Potential. On June 3, Wells Fargo increased the price target on The Pennant Group stock from $30 to $31, keeping its Equal Weight rating on the shares.
